## ğŸ”‘ **Auth & User Management (Shared)**

* `POST /auth/register` â†’ create user (role-based: student/faculty/staff/admin)
* `POST /auth/login` â†’ login, returns JWT
* `POST /auth/logout` â†’ logout, invalidate token
* `GET /auth/me` â†’ current user profile
* `PUT /auth/change-password` â†’ update password
* `POST /auth/forgot-password` â†’ request reset
* `POST /auth/reset-password` â†’ reset with token
* `PUT /users/:id` â†’ update profile (avatar, phone, settings)
* `GET /users/:id` â†’ get user profile by ID
* `GET /users?role=faculty|student|staff|admin` â†’ filter by role

